# zero-arena-bacend hosts two services that DO NOT share configuration:
#
#   • transfer-oracle service  →  copy `.env.transfer-oracle.example` into `.env`
#   • paper           service  →  copy `.env.paper.example`           into `.env`
#
# In production they run on different hosts. They never need to share keys —
# transfer-signer and paper-updater are distinct roles with different threat
# models.
#
# Dataset ingest moved to the SDK: `npx zeroarena dataset ingest …`.
#
# This file is a stub. Do not paste secrets here.
